ombing ever in the Somali capital Mogadishu. October 15, 2017 In "News" A senior Somali commander and six other soldiers died Sunday after a suicide car bomber rammed his car into their military convoy as it travelled through the capital, Mogadishu, a military source said. September 18, 2016 In "News" Several police officers were among at least eight people killed in an attack on a bus in northeast Kenya believed to have been staged by the Somali Islamist Shebaab group, a presidential spokesperson said Saturday. Kenyan President Uhuru Kenyatta had been briefed on the "brutal" murders of eight people, including… December 7, 2019 In "News"